long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a small wrapper to embed the hosted version of GAuth Authenticator in Chrome.

This application generates TOTP tokens for multi-factor authentication used by Google, Dropbox, Amazon and many others.
